servers.description: Sandbox API. Do not send real data
Production API. Contact us for integration.

get.summary: List of addresses belonging to user profile

post.summary: Adds address info to user profile.
post.description: List of required fields are slightly different for different countries. For example state field is required for US, CA, BR and AU addresses but not for other countries. Please look at Addresses.Requirements to figure out which fields are required to create addresses in specific country.

BadRequest.description: Request messege data did not pass validation

Unauthorized.description: Not authorized to access requested data.

Forbidden.description: Access to requested data is forbidden.

Unprocessable.description: Request message data did not pass validation

info.title: TransferWise

post.summary: The first step to a payout
post.description: Quote fetches current mid-market exchange rate that will be used for your transfer. Quote also calculates our fee and estimated delivery time.

200.description: Use the quote id for the transfer

targetAmount.description: amount in target currency - not to be used with source amount

sourceAmount.description: amount is source currency - not to be used with target amount

deliveryEstimate.description: assumes the tranfer will be created now
